{"tid":332160,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"那些年的日劇 原來已經是10多年前","createTime":"2017-07-22T18:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T02:47:50.000Z","uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d342241bce782699484afd3d1756f58fdb04d3ac","tid":332160,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:42:42.000Z","msg":"雖然去年女神新垣結衣的《逃恥》，還是近期播出山下智久的《Code blue 3》、渡邊直美的《最強媽媽栞納》都成功掀起話題，不過無疑其受歡迎程度都不及90年代般厲害，現在聽一次那些年的日劇神曲，不禁令人想起昔日的青春回憶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/024147_72ea29530ad7c26fb9ee922be3bc8075.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F024147_72ea29530ad7c26fb9ee922be3bc8075.jpg&h=2135d6a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家必然說得出《東京愛情故事》、《悠長假期》、《GTO麻辣教師》、《戀愛世紀》等日劇，可是近年日劇逐漸顯露出頹勢，甚至被韓劇佔據大半江山。日本富士電視台曾經接受傳媒訪問時表示過，他們在提拔了一批二十五六歲的年輕人擔任制片人和導演，拍攝了一批深受歡迎的青春偶像劇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/024200_5cafa8fadc1e4dfabe185eb1ca5bc1cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F024200_5cafa8fadc1e4dfabe185eb1ca5bc1cb.jpg&h=d89b0bd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來以木村拓哉、反町隆史、常盤貴子、酒井法子、鈴木保奈美、深田恭子及松隆子等年青偶像掛帥的劇集流行整個華語地區，掀起哈日熱潮。而香港的電視台如無線和亞視大打「日劇戰」，亦有助香港人更為認識日劇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2tQul6V\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2tQul6V&d=3aNSw6jVxEDekNmPJGIa%2BL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=513b967e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2tQul6V</a>"},{"pid":"7bb2ef635fed39a7f0eb9e1b38f5e4f0889885aa","tid":332160,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T19:23:32.000Z","msg":"其實唔可以攞以前收視同而家收視比<br />\n畢竟科技都唔同哂"},{"pid":"287fcf01691a964ed6ad54e955860d1e6d685395","tid":332160,"uid":2781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T23:42:47.000Z","msg":"果啲劇廿年都黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a403e26573254ef3bb08a91030a4373de08ece3c","tid":332160,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T00:01:05.000Z","msg":"龍櫻"},{"pid":"458e3e61b3c76c64552cc89c34a69decba54c352","tid":332160,"uid":109268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T01:38:32.000Z","msg":"想睇返深田恭子套神啊!"},{"pid":"38a2b6f9a24ba4df686d0b210b6dc04c99dd1bae","tid":332160,"uid":130051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T01:39:20.000Z","msg":"求婚大作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7460e0688eb85735bf26a8f74e89f39d405660","tid":332160,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:00:57.000Z","msg":"華麗一族都10年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d867f0fb1bc0a588a687d7ef5ee2a001d64dcf87","tid":332160,"uid":56462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:02:35.000Z","msg":"深田恭子好正"},{"pid":"45071a4eb6bc139f1547f9004f0378270a9fa49a","tid":332160,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:47:50.000Z","msg":"《庶務二課》系列，演打雜嘅主角江角真紀子，竟然係「小員工，大領導」，<br />\n能夠改變企業高層嘅大小決策。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S. 富士電視台於90年代初期，搬遷至當時為新填海地嘅「台場」，因此電視台因乘利便， <br />\n以台場周邊地域作為劇集外景。（例子：彩虹橋）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}